OL,3,CMan charged with murder after assault
OL,4,Cin East Finchley
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter an assault in East Finchley.
OL,9,FTevin Melbourne, 30, of Pittman
OL,10,FGardens, Ilford was charged on Monday,
OL,11,FJuly 20, following the incident.
OL,13,FHe is expected to appear at Croydon
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court later on Monday.
OL,16,FPaul Heyfron, 53, died in hospital on
OL,17,FSunday, 12 July, nearly two weeks
OL,18,Fafter being assaulted inside a shop in
OL,19,FBrook Walk, East Finchley.
